{"type": "article", "id": 20360, "title": "倾斜花瓶", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-07T07:36:37Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607113535BboSYJxwTQaDrnHp.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这一系列花瓶来自日本设计师藤原敬介（keisuke fujiwara），模拟了水滴的形状，是用钢材制作的。插上花之后，花瓶会根据花枝的重量微微倾斜，随着花瓣落下，花瓶又能轻轻摆动，寻找到平衡点，巧妙而有趣味。花瓶系列有 5 种颜色组合，每个花瓶都呈现渐变的镜面效果，在晃动中有了光影的变化。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113534sAoO28iWQdlKGeIx.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113534E1mphjxgb6AV5Bye.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113534EZ6q0sHyrDKJf9Sw.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}